main event: Two circular objects were sighted in the sky traveling at a high speed, appearing to blink on and off at irregular intervals.
interesting points: The objects were described as round and white in color, appearing to be as large as a car,The sighting lasted approximately 2 minutes and occurred at an altitude of about 10,000 feet,The objects were tracked visually as well as on ground radar,Airplanes in the area were checked, and no aircraft were found,The sighting took place near Friendship Airport in Baltimore, MD.
